Hello 👋 I'm Bree.
I'm 32, born HIV+. 

I've been on a journey to rebuild my life and share my experience, despite my fear. 

I love cats, art and writing and I'm currently in school to become a historian. 

I'm committed to sharing my humble piece of life with the world. 
Thanks for being here 💚
I start like when I first started coding - Do a Hello World :)

Fra Lady og Landstrykeren, scenen hvor de spiser spaghetti med kjøttboller sammen, og han dytter den siste kjøttbollen mot henne med nesen.

Et dikt: Hymn for the future
May you always know pain as temporary and laughter better. May the universe bless you with the perseverance to try harder. May you build a kinder history than the ruins you were given. May the greatest gift you receive be more than just a life, but a life where the world is safer, a life so full of love and joy that it is worth living. Nikita Gill
